FIRSTRUN

5 PAUSE

( Definition of an object avoidance program )

( Sensors constants )
1 CONSTANT LEFT-ULTRA
2 CONSTANT CENTER-ULTRA
3 CONSTANT RIGHT-ULTRA

10 Constant MinDistance

( Sensor value storage )
Variable LeftSensor
Variable CenterSensor
Variable RightSensor

: MAIN
  10 0 Do
    10 FORWARD      \ while going forward

    ( Read the ultrasonic sensor values )
    LEFT-ULTRA distance LeftSensor !
    CENTER-ULTRA distance CenterSensor !
    RIGHT-ULTRA distance RightSensor !

    ( always ignore out of range -1 )
    LeftSensor @ DUP -1 = If
     ." Invalid Left value" CR
    else
        MinDistance < If
            1000 RIGHT
    Then

    CenterSensor @ DUP -1 = If
     ." Invalid Center value" cr
    else
        MinDistance < If
            2000 LEFT
    then

    RightSensor @ DUP -1 = If
     ." Invalid Right value" cr
    else
        MinDistance < If
            2000 LEFT
    then

    1 pause
  loop
  stop
  ;


  Main
